{"tid":2239354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尹兆堅警告政府 民主黨會用盡一切辦法阻止明日大嶼","createTime":"2020-10-12T00:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T09:11:15.000Z","uid":30561,"like":33,"dislike":151,"uniUserReply":141,"replies":[{"pid":"251e2edbeb8de26c61bd7a25add875f215454645","tid":2239354,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:40:26.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥將於周三公布新一份《施政報告》，民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅要求政府再向全港市民派發一萬元現金，以及設立臨時失業援助金，並叫停「明日大嶼」計劃，將資源用作救人救市。另外，對於有消息指新一份《施政報告》中會宣布，在內地設立港人投票站，民主黨對此表示強烈反對和憤怒，強調會全力阻止相關法例在立法會通過。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨各支部今日在政府總部外舉行「流水式」示威請願行動，向政府提出多項訴求，當中包括盡快重啟立法會選舉、全力營救被扣押在深圳的12港人回港。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅批評，保就業計劃只保老闆、不保打工仔，故一直要求設立臨時失業援助金，支援因疫情而失業的港人，每月向他們發放9000元、為期半年。他又批評政府一再漠視打工仔的苦況，強烈要求政府趁施政報告推出失業援助金計劃。他重申，政府需要全民派發一萬元現金，以解港人燃眉之急，又需要不分行業，向所有中小微企的實際經營者提供補貼。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅指出，已多次強烈要求政府叫停「明日大嶼」，將資源用作支援百業和失業港人。他重申，「明日大嶼」的造價估算僅按2018年9月價格計算，並非工程的付款當日價格，有嚴重篤數之嫌。現時香港的財政儲備只剩8000多億，但過往多項政府的大白象工程超支延誤均十分嚴重，有理由相信明日大嶼的最終造價勢必超過一萬億，形容是掏空庫房。他警告，政府必須立即收手，否則民主黨會用盡一切辦法，全力阻止該項工程撥款在立法會通過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/QBHZJZX5SFA4HEEJ6KFSNAHFAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FQBHZJZX5SFA4HEEJ6KFSNAHFAM%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=0df6b165\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FQBHZJZX5SFA4HEEJ6KFSNAHFAM%2F&h=b2c515ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/QBHZJZX5SFA4HEEJ6KFSNAHFAM/</a>"},{"pid":"dda0b718570a1d660b322379dad0114166b262df","tid":2239354,"uid":41205,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:40:57.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"e338e514c49200398be2dc457122220974fda0c2","tid":2239354,"uid":290025,"like":88,"dislike":5,"score":83,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:41:12.000Z","msg":"有7用咩,議會人數又唔夠"},{"pid":"923d457c0876e01769a05618d1ef801321b424a8","tid":2239354,"uid":40856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:41:15.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"66c4a7a0e66157ef3bc260159e48b3b82be8bc51","tid":2239354,"uid":362827,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtoKStG.gif&amp;h=e90c3cb1&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"0d2b2dd11227d487df7ed14c15dff80ef0febfe7","tid":2239354,"uid":223198,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:41:57.000Z","msg":"好驚呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9afcdd10de37b86a8ee31efa2b853cc7caf7434","tid":2239354,"uid":95138,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:42:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ab9824f14dc3d7cd7d2ed3c696f9daea7bab445","tid":2239354,"uid":1589,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:43:35.000Z","msg":"Noted with thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c97f2cee10319b26654df82cfe9595475cbec53","tid":2239354,"uid":62749,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:45:13.000Z","msg":"港共 : 黑人問號.jpg"},{"pid":"083144fe58c456b343e33c5ce3b581d43d9fa5f4","tid":2239354,"uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66c4a7a0e66157ef3bc260159e48b3b82be8bc51","tid":2239354,"uid":362827,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtoKStG.gif&amp;h=e90c3cb1&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:48:25.000Z","msg":"立法會係需要認受性<br />\n<br />\n泛民會用盡一切辦法係向全世界傳媒表明，佢地會代表2百幾萬黃絲去阻止明日大嶼通過。"},{"pid":"679b57a4ae112586d542c2c5f5fea57990ca01dc","tid":2239354,"uid":239469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T00:50:28.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"956b037a115c7ae6fad5ec396716b6a30e7833f4","tid":2239354,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12